  "instructions": [
    "heat the vegetable oil in a large pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped scallions and cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "add the grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "add the unroasted peanuts, salt, and soy sauce, and stir to combine.",
    "add 4 cups of water to the pressure cooker, and bring to a boil.",
    "close the lid and cook at high pressure for 10 minutes.",
    "let the pressure release naturally for 5 minutes, then quick-release any remaining pressure.",
    "serve the peanuts hot, garnished with additional scallions if desired."
